item.title: About me
item.description: I’m currently an intern at PocketHealth working in the Data Engineering team. This September, I’ll be going back to the Univeristy of Toronto to finish my degree after completing a total of 16-months of software engineering internships at IBM and PocketHealth.

item.title: Skills
item.description: Some of the server-side technologies I’ve worked with include Golang, Node.js, Python, SQL, and Java. I’ve also enjoyed using Angular with TypeScript as my primary frontend framework.
